name: When are holidays in this year?

speech:

Additional Holidays (University will be closed) on 4th of Jan to 5th of Jan.

Federal Territory Day on 1st of Feb.

Chinese New Year on 12th of Feb to 13 of Feb.

Nuzul Al- Quran on 29th of Apr.

Labour Day on 1st of May.

Hari Raya Puasa - Subject to change (Any changes by the Authorities may alter the Public Holidays) on 13th of May to 14th of May.

Wesak Day on 26th of May.

Birthday of S.P.B. Yang di-Pertuan Agong on 7th of Jun.

Hari Raya Qurban - Subject to change (Any changes by the Authorities may alter the Public Holidays) on 20th of July.

Awal Muharram (Maal Hijrah) on 10th of Aug.

National Day on 31st of Aug.

Malaysia Day on 16th of Sep.

Birthday of Prophet Muhammad S.A.W (Maulidur Rasul) on 19th of Oct.

Deepavali - Subject to change (Any changes by the Authorities may alter the Public Holidays) on 4th of Nov.

Additional Holiday (University will be closed) on 5th of Nov.

Year End Break on 24th of Dec to 9th of Jan.

Christmas Day on 25th of Dec.
